text: Looking for an Off-Grid, private homestead with NO HOA on nearly 30 acres? This is the home for you! Located 3.7 miles down a private dirt road behind a locked gate, you'll find this oasis of serenity and be gauranteed the peace you have been seeking. The community has minimal restrictions ensuring you have the freedom to do what you like with your property while still protecting and preserving the future value of the home and land sites. Surrounded by Junipers and Pinion Pines in the Weaver Mountains, at just under 5,000 ft elevation with great views and a seasonal creek, it's the perfect way to escape the heat and enjoy four mild seasons. 4WD is recommended for the winter months. Built with energy efficiency and great economy in mind, structural insulated panels (SIPS) provide excellent insulation and comfortable climate control. The home is perfectly situated to utilize passive solar for heating and cooling year round but also comes with two cozy propane stoves. The metal roof gives you longevity and reliability. This two story custom home is 3040 sqft PLUS an additional 480 sqft glassed and screened Arizona Room on the upper level and a covered patio below for your relaxation and enjoyment. The open floor plan has beautiful pine cathedral ceilings and a spacious kitchen with granite counter tops and built-in appliances. The island comes with the added bonus of under-counter shelving and built in sink! The upper floor has 3/4" solid red oak flooring and the lower floor and large upstairs laundry room have new solid core plank vinyl flooring. Master bedroom is on main level along with kitchen, laundry, office, and Arizona room. The master bathroom is a 3/4 with walk-in tile shower. On the lower level of the home, you will find a 608 sqft workshop with an overhead door. This could also be used as a tandem 2-car garage. Outside is an oversized detached carport and fenced back yard. Plenty of space in the two-bay covered RV parking! Your garden is irrigated and entirely enclosed in hardware cloth fencing. Large 55 gallon drum has been buried outside to create an in-ground cook pit for your large family gatherings and BBQ events! Grass backyard is fully fenced and well-lit at night with motion sensing lights. The private well is connected to a 5,000 gallon water storage tank and a solar pump. The solar for the well is conveniently placed right next to the well and storage tank. All other solar equipment and batteries are housed in an additional outbuilding. Property was made Firewise in Spring 2023. This would be an ideal location for horses! Clean and well maintained, one owner home - what a unique opportunity! This truly needs to be seen to appreciate it fully.
